            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "徐睿知被爆遭金秀賢使計誣衊終脫污名  節目上意氣風發自嘲︰我擅長情緒勒索",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"徐睿知被爆遭金秀賢使計誣衊終洗脫污名 上節目以醜聞自嘲︰我擅長情緒勒索拍檔\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4190d2ff3abc19a082580506b2516509/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250413/_2025041314550888145.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">徐睿知被爆遭金秀賢使計誣衊終洗脫污名 上節目以醜聞自嘲︰我擅長情緒勒索拍檔</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>5年前憑韓劇《雖然是精神病但沒關係》爆紅的徐睿知，後來因傳出涉校園暴力、欺凌工作人員、虛報學歷、精神操控前男友金正賢等醜聞，以致一度暫停演藝活動，直至去年才正式復出。早前爆發金秀賢與金賽綸爭議期間，有自稱是金秀賢經理人公司GOLDMEDALIST的前員工爆料指，當年其實是金秀賢和其表哥李沙朗為掩蓋自己的醜聞，於是拿當時仍在該公司旗下的徐睿知作擋箭牌，請人造謠抹黑她成「恐怖情人」，圖轉移視線。及後徐睿知現時的經理人公司Sublime亦正式起訴涉嫌造謠誣衊她的前工作人員。\n\n</p><h2>徐睿知拿舊日醜聞搞笑</h2>\n<p>終於洗清惡名的徐睿知昨晚（12日）為綜藝騷《SNL Korea》（韓國版《周末直播》）擔任嘉賓主持，就大方地拿舊日醜聞來搞笑。甫出場時，時隔8年首度演出綜藝騷的她坦言自覺緊張，但會努力表演。被問到怎樣表現其決心時，她說︰「我會操控所有拍檔的情緒，讓大家覺得很有趣……」主持人申東燁即附和道︰「對，精神操控是你的專長和愛好。」接着即問誰想成為徐睿知的「受害者」，一眾節目組演員即全體舉手喊道︰「我！我！我！」此外，在趣劇《夏娃的美容院》中，徐睿知為金元勳洗頭時，更以「金僵硬」（在短訊中對舊愛金正賢的暱稱）來大放笑彈，指金元勳的頸部很「僵硬」。在《害羞的睿知妹》中又飾演謊稱母胎單身的綠茶婊，被揭發後說：「因為都說理想型是純潔的女人，所以我裝作無辜。大家都知道，我在說謊。」此段對白被指影射其虛報學歷的傳聞。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關文章︰<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/film-drama/%E5%BD%B1%E8%A6%96%E5%9C%88\">金賽綸逝世｜金秀賢「在金賽綸家中親暱片」曝光！女方享受男方撫摸 金賽綸家人為照片進行科學鑑證</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192719/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"徐睿知任韓國版《周末直播》嘉賓主持，頻頻以舊日負面新聞當笑料。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5da485af0ff17d3ce52f905092b96b51/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-13_at_12_53_12.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐睿知任韓國版《周末直播》嘉賓主持，頻頻以舊日負面新聞當笑料。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192720/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"徐睿知笑言要精神操控節目組所有演員，申東燁即問誰想做受害者。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/61d76afad21034d9f71037f90eac271c/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-13_at_12_53_36.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐睿知笑言要精神操控節目組所有演員，申東燁即問誰想做受害者。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192721/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"結果節目組所有男諧星爭住舉手要「被害」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/97acc6db63c4ea3cb3ad7eaa921012c9/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-13_at_12_54_00.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        結果節目組所有男諧星爭住舉手要「被害」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192722/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"在趣劇《夏娃的美容院》中，徐睿知扮演愛操控人的「惡魔老闆娘」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/442d0a602f3cdf5e397bf8b66b4c5ddb/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-13_at_12_54_27.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        在趣劇《夏娃的美容院》中，徐睿知扮演愛操控人的「惡魔老闆娘」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192723/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"以舊愛金正賢花名「金僵硬」來搞笑，指金元勳的頸部很「僵硬」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/205bd69cb562f2fa7ab84931e1386873/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-13_at_12_54_57.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        以舊愛金正賢花名「金僵硬」來搞笑，指金元勳的頸部很「僵硬」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192724/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"徐睿知在趣劇中扮演綠茶婊，疑似影射其被指虛報學歷的醜聞。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7e1e7e502459368ed28fc230972d2545/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-13_at_12_55_38.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐睿知在趣劇中扮演綠茶婊，疑似影射其被指虛報學歷的醜聞。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192725/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"在以GPT為主題的趣劇中，徐睿知被指借對白申訴當年被誣衊的辛酸。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d98c431b56bd0b3cc301e1cd6541fd3b/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-13_at_12_56_15.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        在以GPT為主題的趣劇中，徐睿知被指借對白申訴當年被誣衊的辛酸。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192726/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"當年徐睿知爆紅後即被頻傳黑料，早前傳出是金秀員請人造謠誣衊她。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/879ee6739d8f0f4d21299b0a40a8c382/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-13_at_12_57_01.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當年徐睿知爆紅後即被頻傳黑料，早前傳出是金秀員請人造謠誣衊她。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192727/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"及後D社又爆料指徐睿知操控當時的男友金正賢，令他刻意冷待拍檔徐玄。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/da3d5c2b0c556fcb3133dd5c28c26b56/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-13_at_12_57_33.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        及後D社又爆料指徐睿知操控當時的男友金正賢，令他刻意冷待拍檔徐玄。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192730/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"徐睿知與金秀賢合作而爆紅。（《雖然是精神病但沒關係》劇照）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1f62ba5d3c34e12536352a1a10600b23/2025-04/kim_2.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐睿知與金秀賢合作而爆紅。（《雖然是精神病但沒關係》劇照）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192731/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《雖然是精神病但沒關係》劇照\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8b2a962221dfe8ce40a22f04d93101c3/2025-04/1_28.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《雖然是精神病但沒關係》劇照\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4192738/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"徐睿知5年前憑韓劇《雖然是精神病但沒關係》爆紅。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f14eb9c85a116296e5cf4c2a36ac92b2/2025-04/12_0_4.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        徐睿知5年前憑韓劇《雖然是精神病但沒關係》爆紅。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>徐睿知以GPT趣劇發聲</h2>\n<p>在以GPT為主題的趣劇中，徐睿知對被同事們講閒話的金元勳說：「最讓人鬱悶的就是靜靜地坐着，被人無視，甚麼話都說不出來，這太不公平了。」金元勳就問她：「你怎麼知道這麼多？」徐睿知答道：「我也經歷了很多。」這一整段對白則被解讀為徐睿知對圍繞她的一系列爭議作回應。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
