            "title": "跳水｜全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀 續受體重影響 但已滿意表現",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。世界泳聯官方微博圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/fa2fc9e2492313787ba6545fa52484d1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250413/_2025041314475934939.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。世界泳聯官方微博圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>國家跳水名將全紅嬋繼上周跳水世界盃墨西哥站失準得銀牌後，周六加拿大溫莎站女子單人10公台決賽再次失準屈居隊友陳芋汐之後得亞軍。全紅嬋賽後直言體重漲了需要適應，但仍頗滿意自己表現。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。世界泳聯官方微博圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4f504224752f3386038acf60999957e0/2025-04/c71ed440gy1i0epss0m7cj24eh2xn1l0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。世界泳聯官方微博圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳芋汐奪金。世界泳聯官方微博圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/84f3201208924ddd2a9c0bed003380c0/2025-04/c71ed440gy1i0epsv7g68j24ii30cx6r.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳芋汐奪金。世界泳聯官方微博圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。新華社資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/adbd604aaa28513ce3dc5b25e0e40161/2025-04/XxjpseC007170_20250406_PEPFN0A001_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。新華社資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。新華社資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1cd191e395ed04dc50d4d63e2a47fab2/2025-04/XxjpseC007175_20250406_PEPFN0A001.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。新華社資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。新華社資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5f94b6941a89e3b832e9606bf77eb5b7/2025-04/XxjpseC007174_20250406_PEPFN0A001.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。新華社資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。新華社資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/10e3a29ced613cbd8b62a1a8da685b41/2025-04/XxjpseC007178_20250406_PEPFN0A001_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀。新華社資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀</h2>\n<p>上場墨西哥站乃全紅嬋18歲後首戰，她受發育增重影響下失準摘銀。今場她的表現明顯有所提升，於前三輪都破80分，以總分256.80分排第一，領先次席的陳芋汐18.05分。然而，全紅嬋於第4輪的207C出現大失誤只得64.35分，而陳芋汐則跳出全場最高的92.40分，一下子反超前。第5跳兩人同分下，陳芋汐終以10分優勢奪金。\n\n</p><h2>「體重漲了」</h2>\n<p>連續兩站得亞後，全紅嬋直認：「體重漲了，確實是漲了，可能還是要有一個適應期，適應了這段時期，後邊可能就會平穩了。對於本場比賽，我覺得還挺滿意的，感覺有點不可思議，平時訓練的時候也沒跳這麼好。」陳芋汐則喜言：「以前比賽前可能會比較緊張，現在來說好了一點，能更多專注在自己的動作上。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063685/即時-體育-跳水-全紅嬋連續兩站失準摘銀-續受體重影響-但已滿意表現",
