            "title": "亞洲羽毛球錦標賽｜鄧謝配擊敗日本組合 首奪亞錦賽冠軍",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"鄧謝配擊敗日本組合，首奪亞錦賽冠軍。新華社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5a74aef0d63d4945ff024e3efe464f9a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250413/_2025041315071445707.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">鄧謝配擊敗日本組合，首奪亞錦賽冠軍。新華社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>香港混雙組合鄧俊文、謝影雪，周日在寧波舉行的亞洲羽毛球錦標賽混雙決賽，與世界排名11的日本組合綠川大輝、齋藤夏激戰3盤，以21:15、17:21、21:13，局數2:1力挫日本組合，鄧謝配首次在亞錦賽封王。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄧俊文、謝影雪混雙決賽硬撼日本組合。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dfaba15566d9943e0fed41d87018df42/2025-04/XxjpseC007151_20250412_PEPFN0A001.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧俊文、謝影雪混雙決賽硬撼日本組合。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄧俊文、謝影雪混雙決賽硬撼日本組合。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6cfa81887714f8d7b0b20267f8ccb277/2025-04/XxjpseC007152_20250412_PEPFN0A001_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧俊文、謝影雪混雙決賽硬撼日本組合。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"鄧俊文、謝影雪混雙決賽硬撼日本組合。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8a7295f6b832a3a63f9beb3cda2c8fea/2025-04/XxjpseC007156_20250412_PEPFN0A001_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧俊文、謝影雪混雙決賽硬撼日本組合。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063691/即時-體育-亞洲羽毛球錦標賽-鄧謝配擊敗日本組合-首奪亞錦賽冠軍",
